OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FGiving birth is often the happiest day
OL,8,Fof any mother's life and learning
OL,9,Fyou've got cancer can be the most
OL,10,Fdevastating - but hundreds of women a
OL,11,Fyear go through those life-changing
OL,12,Fexperiences at around the same time.
OL,14,FAround two women a day are diagnosed
OL,15,Fwith cancer during pregnancy or soon
OL,16,Fafter, according to Mummy's Star
OL,17,Fcharity, with many being forced to use
OL,18,Ftheir maternity leave to get treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FThat is because there is no additional
OL,8,Fstatutory sick or maternity leave for
OL,9,Fmothers in that situation, meaning
OL,10,Fthey feel like they're being made to
OL,11,Fchoose between their own health and
OL,12,Fbonding with their baby.
OL,14,F"I felt like I wasn't a mum," Ashleigh
OL,15,FEccles, who was diagnosed with cancer
OL,16,F12 days after giving birth, told ITV
OL,17,FNews.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,F"While I was fighting for my life,"
OL,8,Fshe said, "I should have been having
OL,9,Fsnuggles with my baby and enjoying
OL,10,Fthat really enriching time where
OL,11,Fyou're able to form a bond and have
OL,12,Fall these lovely moments.
OL,14,F"Actually, I was having to leave my
OL,15,Fbaby with my parents and go for five-
OL,16,Fhour chemo sessions, go for overnights
OL,17,Fin hospital."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FMothers like Ashley are now
OL,8,Fcampaigning for a law change which
OL,9,Fwould allow them to defer their
OL,10,Fmaternity leave for up to a year so
OL,11,Fthey can go through treatment.
OL,13,FBeth Dedman assumed she'd be able to
OL,14,Fdefer her maternity leave when she was
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with cancer, when her baby
OL,16,Fwas four months old.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,F"I began chemotherapy pretty much
OL,8,Fstraight away, for seven months, which
OL,9,Fmeant I had to spend a lot of time
OL,10,Faway from my daughter whilst I
OL,11,Freceived treatment," she told ITV News.
OL,13,F"I was left quite unwell during
OL,14,Ftreatment, which meant my mum, my
OL,15,Fpartner and other family had to help
OL,16,Fcare for her, which was really
OL,17,Fupsetting."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FDuring treatment, she began looking
OL,8,Finto how she could defer her maternity
OL,9,Fleave and was "angry" to find out
OL,10,F"there was nothing that they could do
OL,11,Fto help me, and there was no support -
OL,12,Fgovernment-wise. You fall into this
OL,13,Fgap where you're not catered for."
OL,15,FThe government is currently reviewing
OL,16,Fparental leave and will start making
OL,17,Fany changes in early 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FBeth said being allowed to defer her
OL,8,Fmaternity leave would have made all
OL,9,Fthe difference to her mental health
OL,10,Fwhile going through treatment.
OL,12,F"Emotionally, it would have just
OL,13,Falleviated so much stress and worry
OL,14,Fand anger. I was already angry that
OL,15,FI'd been diagnosed with cancer, but
OL,16,Fthe anger of then not being able to do
OL,17,Fanything with my leave made everything
OL,18,Fso much more heightened."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FAshleigh said the ability to defer
OL,8,Fwould have "given me a little bit of
OL,9,Fhope in those really dark moments".
OL,11,F"I would have been able to relax a bit
OL,12,Fmore during that period of time and
OL,13,Fdeal with things as they hit me a
OL,14,Flittle bit more instead of panicking
OL,15,Fthat 'this is my only chance'.
OL,17,F"My fertility was affected by my
OL,18,Ftreatment. It's not now possible for
OL,19,Fme to have any children. So that was
OL,20,Fmy one and only time to have those
OL,21,Fbonding experiences."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FPete Wallroth started the Mummy's Star
OL,8,Fcharity to support mothers in that
OL,9,Fsituation after his wife died three
OL,10,Fmonths after giving birth to their son.
OL,12,F"In the early weeks after our son
OL,13,Farrived, she was reluctant at times to
OL,14,Feven hold him because she was so
OL,15,Fworried about the impacts of chemo-
OL,16,Frelated fatigue," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,F"She was just so worried about her own
OL,8,Fphysical ability to be able to be part
OL,9,Fof his life in those early weeks. From
OL,10,Fa partner's perspective, that is
OL,11,Fabsolutely heartbreaking to watch the
OL,12,Fperson that you love not be able to
OL,13,Ffully participate in something that
OL,14,Fevery family deserves to have," he
OL,15,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FHe added: "All of a sudden, that skin-
OL,8,Fto-skin time with your baby is
OL,9,Finterrupted. The opportunity to
OL,10,Fbreastfeed your child is interrupted.
OL,11,FAnd there's so much grief the families
OL,12,Fexperience in that period of time.
OL,14,F"But it's on a descending timeline
OL,15,Fconstantly because that maternity
OL,16,Fleave has commenced. No matter what's
OL,17,Fgoing on, no matter what the outcome
OL,18,Flikely in the future of your own
OL,19,Fcancer diagnosis - when that maternity
OL,20,Fleave ends, it's gone and it's gone
OL,21,Fforever."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FHe accepted that allowing maternity
OL,8,Fleave deferments would involve a
OL,9,F"short-term cost" to the taxpayer but
OL,10,Fsaid that would be recouped by mothers
OL,11,Freturning to work with much improved
OL,12,Fmental health, meaning they would be
OL,13,Fable to contribute to the economy more
OL,14,Feffectively.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FA survey by Mummy's Star last year
OL,8,Ffound that 70% of mothers diagnosed
OL,9,Fwith cancer during or after pregnancy
OL,10,Fthought the experience impacted their
OL,11,Fability to bond with their child, 91%
OL,12,Fsaid cancer affected their confidence
OL,13,Fas a parent and 75% experienced
OL,14,Fincreased perinatal mental health
OL,15,Fchallenges, including anxiety,
OL,16,Fdepression, or suicidal thoughts.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FIreland passed legislation allowing
OL,8,Fmums to defer maternity leave during
OL,9,Fcancer treatment in 2024, following
OL,10,Fcampaigning from the Irish Cancer
OL,11,FSociety.
OL,13,FThe amendment was hailed by Minister
OL,14,FRoderic O'Gorman as "a small, simple
OL,15,Fchange that will have a big impact for
OL,16,Fso many women at a very challenging
OL,17,Ftime in their lives".
OL,19,FMummy's Star is now urging the UK
OL,20,Fgovernment to follow suit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774015868
OL,3,C'I gave birth then got cancer': Mums
OL,4,Cdemand the right to pause maternity
OL,5,Cleave
OL,7,FA Department for Work and Pensions
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "We are committed
OL,9,Fto improving the parental leave and
OL,10,Fpay system for working families and
OL,11,Fbusinesses.
OL,13,F"Our Parental Leave and Pay Review
OL,14,Fwhich runs until early 2027 is
OL,15,Fconsidering all leave and pay
OL,16,Fentitlements to assess whether the
OL,17,Fsupport available meets the needs of
OL,18,Fmodern working families."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
